Ctrl+,:Set Global Variables:‾ 3264:// =====================‾0D‾0A// GLOBAL VARIABLES‾0D
‾0A// Group: Global controls & config‾0D‾0A// =====
================‾0D‾0A//‾0D‾0A// Notes:‾0D‾0A// - D
o NOT change this script's name.‾0D‾0A// - If you u
pdate any global variables, re-run this script‾0D‾0A
