nity and derived prices ----‾0D‾0A$bid    = BID;‾0D
‾0A$ask    = ASK;‾0D‾0A$spread = $ask - $bid;‾0D‾0A
‾0D‾0Aif ($bid <= 0 || $ask <= 0 || $spread < 0) {‾0D
‾0A    MsgBox("Quote sanity failed for " + Symbol +
