p < 0.25 || $bid < 0.25 || $ask < 0.25) { $inc = 0.
0005; }‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// ---- Step 1: Slippage-aware s
pread/stop safety (longs) ----‾0D‾0A$stopVsBidFail 
