e profit‾0D‾0A// =====================‾0D‾0A// Buil
ds a TP alert from $stopLossTrigger, $takeProfitFac
tor, and $takeProfitSize.‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// ---- Step 1
: Focus Primary_OE ----‾0D‾0AFocusWindow Primary_OE
;‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// ---- Step 2: Load profit factor (R 
multiple) ----‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// Effective TP distance 
in dollars per share‾0D‾0A$tpDist = $stopLossTrigge
r * $takeProfitFactor;‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// ---- Step 3: L
oad montage context ----‾0D‾0A$mySym = Symbol;‾0D‾0A
$myAcc = Account;‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A$accObj = GetAccountOb
j($myAcc);‾0D‾0A$posNow = $accObj.GetPosition($mySy
m).Share;‾0D‾0A$avgNow = AvgCost;‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// No 
position: nothing to alert.‾0D‾0Aif ($posNow == 0) 
{ return; }‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// If AvgCost still initiali
zing, fall back to last sale‾0D‾0Aif ($avgNow <= 0)
 { $avgNow = Last; }‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// ---- Step 4: Com
pute the target price ----‾0D‾0A$tpPx = $avgNow;‾0D
‾0Aif ($posNow > 0) {‾0D‾0A    // Long: take partia
l when price goes up by TP distance.‾0D‾0A    $tpPx
 = $avgNow + $tpDist;‾0D‾0A} else {‾0D‾0A    // Sho
rt: take partial when price goes down by TP distanc
e.‾0D‾0A    $tpPx = $avgNow - $tpDist;‾0D‾0A}‾0D‾0A
‾0D‾0A// ---- Step 5: Tick-size resolution and snap
ping ----‾0D‾0A$inc = 0.01;‾0D‾0Aif ($tpPx < 1 || $
avgNow < 1)       { $inc = 0.001; }‾0D‾0Aif ($tpPx 
< 0.25 || $avgNow < 0.25) { $inc = 0.0005; }‾0D‾0A$
tpPx = Round($tpPx, 102, $inc);‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// ---- 
Step 6: Remove existing TP alert for this symbol/fa
ctor ----‾0D‾0A$alertName = "TP " + $takeProfitFact
or + "R Partial " + $mySym;‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A$toDel = Get
AlertObj($alertName);‾0D‾0Aif (IsObj($toDel)) { $to
